Process called "record_resource_contention" that takes swarm as Swarm and agent_id as String and outcome as String returns Swarm

Process called "record_agent_creation" that takes swarm as Swarm and agent_id as String returns Swarm

Process called "record_agent_retirement" that takes swarm as Swarm and agent_id as String returns Swarm

Note: Utility Processes
Process called "generate_uuid" returns String

Process called "calculate_event_hash" that takes event as Dictionary[String, Any] returns String

Process called "get_current_timestamp" returns Number

